projectInfo.title: ISU Fashion Show
projectInfo.summary: DTG patterns & ideas for Love-themed Fashion Show
projectInfo.introduction: These are concepts for direct to garment (DTG) prints and screen prints pieces for the 2016 ISU Fashion Show. I used seamless patterns to give a twist on minimalist and futuristic clothing.
